name: BetterDisneyPixar
description:
Been a fan of the Disney/Pixar style for a while and wanted to merge my own, feel like this one came out fairly well and has a decent amount of characters apparently built in already. Primarily for female characters and doesn't do Furry well, or even Kemonomimi more than the ears very well.

Capable of decent NSFW but not specifically made for it.

modelVersions.name: BDP v1.0
modelVersions.description: Mix of an old Disney/Pixar 1.0 model, a personal ConsistentColorful blend, and YiffyMix3. Even so, doesn't do furry very well even with the yiffymix in there.
